data.text:
Celebrate the spooky charm of Halloween Town with this exclusive Funko POP of Jack Skellington, autographed by the legendary Chris Sarandon. Known for his iconic role as the voice of Jack Skellington in Tim Burton's The Nightmare Before Christmas, Sarandon’s signature makes this collectible a must-have for fans of the beloved film and Funko enthusiasts alike.
